  <scopecontent id="aspace_52daec9c350f99e250d4719cb628686a">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Glass negatives of dairy barns, cheesemaking, and dairy science.</p><p> Includes "Food Science Facts" (1981-1984) , Food Science Club files, including its newsletter (1974-1993) , booklets listing Food Science Graduates (1990-1995) and other information pertaining to the Institute of Food Science.</p><p> Also faculty meeting minutes (1986-1990); Dept. Research Projects (1986, 1988), dept. brochures and other department files from the 1980s and a video "A Matter of Judgement: The Case for Food Safety in the Supermarket Deli."</p>  </scopecontent>
